	<li><a href="https://www.epa.gov/sunsafety/uv-index-1">NOAA and EPA UV Index Forecast</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/stratosphere/uv_index/uv_current_map.shtml">Map of Danger Areas</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/stratosphere/uv_index/bulletin.txt">Text List of UV Levels by City</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/stratosphere/uv_index/uv_meanmax.shtml">Monthly Means and Maximums</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/stratosphere/uv_index/uv_annual.shtml">Annual Time Series of UV Index Forecasts</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://www.cpc.ncep.noaa.gov/products/stratosphere/uv_index/Bulletin/">Past UV Bulletins</a></li>
